Nth Even Number
Create a function that takes a number n and returns the nth even number.

Examples
nthEven(1) ➞ 0
// 0 is first even number

nthEven(2) ➞ 2
// 2 is second even number

nthEven(100) ➞ 198

https://edabit.com/challenge/Yj2QWQG7oHREM6DRo

My Solution

function nthEven(n) {
	return (n * 2) - 2
}
